title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part  10] Minimal Synth
description:
Now sharing 4 rare minimal synth lps for those who can&#039;t get enough of this genre! 

To people who have put in a request: I have not forgotten you. I will post them if I happen to have the whole lp. sometimes I only have singles and most of the times the reason is that some of those bands/singers were one-single-wonders lol [miles away from one-hit-wonders]. Curious to find out what&#039;s here? ok:


Bollock Brothers - The Last Supper (1983)

Bourbonese Qualk - Preparing For Power (1986)

Nine Circles - Nine Circles (1982)

Xex - Group Xex (1980)
